game_info.title: Funny Fruits: Merge and Gather Watermelon

games.description: Merge the cheerful fruits, combine them to help them evolve into something even tastier! Hurry to gather more of them to prevent the box from overflowing. Can you collect all the fruits and grow a huge watermelon? Compete with friends for higher scores!
games.instructions: CONTROLS: Use the mouse to move fruits. Click on the game field to release a fruit. GAME RULES: When two fruits of the same type touch, they merge into a larger fruit of the next level. If the fruits overflow the box, the game ends.

games.description: This is a fascinating word puzzle game based on cryptograms. In the game, it is necessary to decipher words using numerical encoding. The gameplay is designed for sequential completion of levels, where each level is a quote or motivational saying. The game allows you to train your attention. A great way to have a pleasant time.
games.instructions: You need to decipher quotes that consist of words. The deciphering is done letter by letter. Each letter corresponds to a number. It is necessary to insert letters into the free slots, relying on the numerical encoding of letters that are already revealed on the game field. Some letters will need to be deciphered from the context. To insert a letter into a slot, you need to tap on the slot and select a letter, using the keyboard directly on the game field.

games.description: A malfunction occurred in the aquarium filter pipes. The fish in the aquarium are in a very difficult situation. If you do not repair all the pipes within 1 minute, you may cause them to disappear. You should fix the pipes as soon as possible to solve the problem.
games.instructions: Play with mouse

games.description: Turbo Truck Race, an intense racing game with diverse trucks, unique abilities, and action-packed modes. Experience the adrenaline with realistic graphics, strategic gameplay, and the freedom to explore different landscapes in FreeMap mode. Turbo Truck Race brings a new level of excitement with powerful trucks!
games.instructions: Player 1 Movement: WASD or arrow keys. Nitro: Left Shift To connect the trailer: T Camera: C Player 2 Movement: arrow keys Nitro: Right Shift To connect the trailer: K Camera: M

games.description: The cute dinosaur wants to reach the exit by eating Sandwich in the area protected by robots. If you want to help him, try to pass the levels by using laser traps without entering the robots' field of vision.
games.instructions: Use WASD or ARROW KEYS control the Dinosaur.

games.description: Doomsday Survival Rpg Shooter is a 2D side-scrolling survival RPG shooting game. Zombies occupy the whole city. You need to recruit the last survivors to fight against zombies for a living. As humans, you need weapons, ammo, food, and medicines. Send your teammates to dispatch different buildings, go to complete the tasks in this fallen town. Time is your life, get out of the safe house and find resources!
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

basic_info.name: Mr. Dude: King of the Hill

game_info.title: Mr. Dude: King of the Hill

games.description: The famous criminal Mister Dude found himself on the top of a mountain, where residents were waiting for him, ready to hand him over to the police. Help him avoid getting caught, defeat all enemies and conquer the mountain! Game Features: Your goal is to knock out, drag and throw your opponents using physics and fun ragdoll effects. The game has a huge number of different objects that you can manipulate and throw at your opponents, different enemies, levels and modes.
games.instructions: Control (computer): WASD, arrows - movement Space - jump, wake up F - pick up an item G - eat food E - climb Q - inventory Left mouse button - hit/throw/shot Right mouse button - aim 1, 2 - switching items Control (mobile devices): Buttons on the screen

games.description: Merge in Space is a cosmic twist on the classic Tetris formula, where you must strategically merge falling astronomical objects of the same kind as they descend through the infinite void of space
games.instructions: Tap or click to drop the object

games.description: 'Sunny Link' is an easy and fun game where players match tiles with summer icons. The goal is to connect two identical tiles. Tiles can be linked if you can join them with three or fewer straight lines. The game has many levels to enjoy. As you play, you’ll hear sounds of the sea. It’s perfect for relaxing and having fun in the sun!
games.instructions: Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game.

games.description: Knife Up 3D is a casual game that tests your reflexes. Feel the rhythm, don't damage the ball and beat your opponents. You can unlock new skins with the rewards you get by passing the levels. It's time to test your reflexes, so if you find it interesting, don't forget to share it with your friends and join in! Have fun!
games.instructions: Click or tap to play

games.description: An exciting puzzle game in which the player will have to help stick make a daring escape from prison. Stick found himself in a sinister prison, from which there is no way out, except for various ingenious paths, hidden objects and puzzles. The player will explore the various rooms of the prison, paying attention to every small detail and examining objects in search of key clues. Each room is filled with riddles, traps and various items that can be used to escape.
games.instructions: The main task of the player is to choose the right items and use them correctly on the screen to go through all the challenges that stand in the way of freedom. Incorrect choices can lead to fatal consequences, so the player must be careful and attentive.

games.description: Hexa Sort 3D mixes puzzle challenges, strategic matching and a satisfying merging experience.Involving clever puzzle-solving and logical manoeuvres, this game is ideal for those seeking a mental workout. As the levels progress, players will find the game both addictive and calming, striking the perfect balance between challenge and relaxation. Put your skills to the test with tasks such as sorting, stacking and merging hexagonal tiles.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Creative and unique puzzle. Fix your avatar's face. Collect all the puzzles of beautiful characters. Avatars from anime to Vikings from cute girls to tough knights. Have a fun and train your brain, memory and logic. Meditative and relaxing game play.
games.instructions: Restore your avatar face to its correct form by moving the dots on the picture. Control by touch on mobile devices or mouse on PC.

games.description: Brand new girl games are already waiting for you! Start creating your own coloring pages by dressing up dolls and painting pictures for backgrounds. You’ll get hundreds of color options, textures and patterns, glitter and gradients. Create your coloring book from scratch, color dresses, and improve your clothes designer skills. If you like drawing that’s the free coloring apps you’ve been looking for! ?️Creative Coloring Games for Girls? ✪ Play as a doll designer: select hair, dress up, and pick accessories ✪ Design clothes: use gradients, textures, and patterns ✪ Combine stylish looks and haircuts like in famous girl games ✪ Color without numbers and paint with glitter ✪ Create coloring pages: move and change dolls and backgrounds ✪ Zoom in and out for better results ✪ Makeover dolls and backgrounds ✪ Paint wallpaper for your phone in fun color games ✪ Take pictures right in the game and share them with friends easily ✪ Free coloring book offline with many options
games.instructions: Use left mouse click to change outfit.

games.description: In Digital Circus Run, the mysterious Caine creates casual parkour and endless running courses that you must traverse. In this virtual circus, you must assist the captives in escaping by navigating them through increasingly difficult stages. As you lead Pomni around the virtual circus, your abilities will be challenged.
games.instructions: Instructions: Complete the game levels and jump at the right time to avoid falling into traps or colliding with enemies and dangerous objects. Use mouse click to start and jump. Double click to jump higher. Tap the screen to jump and double tap to jump higher.

games.description: Join the daily story of the toilet boy in the monster letter world. This new pin pulling game is for you. Let's explore Alphabet Lore with extraordinary characters! In the land of evil letters, you will have a chance to meet various amazing characters and powers of them: evil B ready to punch in your face, Angry C biting with sharp teeth, boring F with a gun, Crazy Z with fire, monster D who loves lava ....
games.instructions: GAMEPLAY ● Your goal is to help the boy get to the toilet or help him get the toilet paper ● Pull the pin in the right order to defeat Alphabet lore monsters with rock, ice or fire ● Collect the coin to buy more clothes and stuffs for the little boy

games.description: Crazy Alien Adventure is an addictive and exciting game. You will play as a brave character who runs, jumps, and dashes through various worlds, collecting stars and power-ups along the way. Your goal is to rescue the animals that are trapped in cages by smashing the wooden stakes with your rush power. The more you run, the more points you get. You can also use the stars to buy items and outfits. Discover different kinds of animals in the game and try to save them all. How far can you go?
games.instructions: W = jump S = fall D = boost

games.description: Solitaire Farm: Seasons 3, the highly anticipated sequel, continues the charming farm theme of Seasons 1 and 2 with incredible 3,400+ levels! Train your brain with diverse solitaire puzzles while enjoying country life. Explore new scenes and travel to new countries. Grow new crops such as Gooseberry, Foxgloves, Celery, Papyrus, Loquat, Prickly Pears, Berseem, and Blackberries. Enjoy stunning visuals and engaging gameplay in this delightful solitaire adventure!
games.instructions: Move cards one point higher or lower than the discard stack, clearing cards to reveal new ones. If stuck, draw from the spare stack. Between levels, manage your farm: plant crops, harvest for coins, unlock features, complete daily missions, spin the Wheel of Fortune, and customize your farmhouse. Return daily for rewards!

games.description: Welcome to the Bffs Spring Break Fashionista. Spring break is here. Barbie and their friends are can’t wait to have some fun together. They’ve been waiting for the spring break since the beginning of the year. Help them prepare their spring break outfits! They can finally wear skirts and dresses since it’s really warm outside now, so make sure to create a cute look! Have fun!
games.instructions: Left Mouse Button Click

games.description: Skill game, classic mode from your favorite games right in the browser on your computer and phone! More levels, more mechanics and new hardcore mode await for you
games.instructions: Desktop: • SPACE - jump • WASD - move • L. SHIFT - running • Double Escape - Menu Mobile: • Touch

games.description: Dot By Dot is a relaxing puzzle game where you have to connect dots into lines and get amazing drawings. Once you connect all the dots and lines, the drawing will be automatically colored! Enjoy the addictive puzzle game! Let the Dot by Dot game develop your creativity and skills. Draw a line, connect colored dots and see what kind of drawing you get.
games.instructions: - Solve simple puzzles - Simple controls, connect the dots by tapping on the screen in the right order - Connect the dots, draw lines to make a whole picture. - Pass a lot of interesting levels and draw a lot of pictures

games.description: Strike Breakout is an intense rescue mission game where you're part of a specialized team sent to save the President and his security officers. You ride shotgun with a skilled helicopter pilot as you embark on a series of 10 nail-biting missions. Each mission drops you into enemy territory where you must stealthily navigate through enemy defenses, neutralize threats, and rescue the hostages.
games.instructions: - Left Mouse to Shot - Right Mouse button for Scope - E to Pick UP and rescue - 1,2,3,4,5 to change weapon

games.description: Puppy Merge is a unique merge game where you must grab and combine identical puppies to create a new and bigger one. Puppies will fall automatically into the arena; what you must do is drag the puppies around and merge them into identical ones. Don't let the puppies fall outside the box, or the game will end. You can try to catch the puppy and bring it back to the arena if the puppy falls.
games.instructions: Drag the left mouse button to move the puppies.

games.description: An addictive block puzzle game that helps train your eyes and brain. It is a combination between the Tetris and Jewels game styles.
games.instructions: Drag the jewel blocks to the desired places, to form full jewel lines (horizontal or vertical) in order to blast them.

games.description: Cute pets need protection, would you like to help them? Draw protection walls for bees coming from different locations in each level and stop them. In levels you find difficult, you can get hints or skip the level directly. You can play Save My Pet Party game in 1 Player or 2 Player modes.
games.instructions: In single player game mode: Use "MOUSE" and "LEFT-CLICK" to draw. In 2 player game mode: Player 1: Use "W,A,S,D" and "E" to draw. Player 2: Use "ARROW KEYS" and "L" to draw.

games.description: Want to feel like a super agent? Jump into a plane with your car! Race against time, perform crazy stunts, and wreak havoc in this insane game. Buckle up and put the pedal to the metal! Explore dozens of locations and vehicles. One wrong move and you're gone! Hurry, you've got a plane to catch!
games.instructions: Use the Mouse button to launch and control the boost.

games.description: Welcome to the world of the future, where style and survival go hand in hand. Help the girl create unique outfits that combine elements of post-apocalyptic chaos and steampunk technology. From armored corsets to steam accessories - the possibilities for customizing clothes in the game are extensive. Get a boost of energy for creativity and self-expression in a world where, even after the end of the world, style remains important for survival!
games.instructions: Together with the main character, we are transported to the post-apocalyptic world of the future. We help the girl to adapt to this world and find her place in it. The result can be saved as a PNG image. Depending on the gaming device, a computer mouse click or a simple touch on touch screens is used to control it.

games.description: Embark on an exhilarating adventure in this arcade runner game! Your goal is simple: Tap to move forward or change direction. Navigate your way through the path, aiming for higher scores as you pave the way!
games.instructions: Tap or click with the right mouse button to change the direction.

games.description: Get your basket ready and save all the eggs you can from a terrible fate. Make sure to empty a full basket into the store. Watch out for the rising quota for eggs each day!
games.instructions: Catch as many eggs as you can with your basket. Sell the eggs in the shop and use the money for upgrades and multipliers to sell eggs faster. Survive the day by catching at least the minimum amount of eggs required.

games.description: Guide Frogga across a busy road in this exciting frogger-style game. Tap to make Frogga jump forward, timing your movements carefully to avoid the oncoming traffic. Each level presents new challenges with faster cars and trickier obstacles, keeping you on your toes. Collect bonuses and power-ups along the way to help Frogga on his journey.
games.instructions: Help Frogga jump across the road and avoid getting squashed in this frogger-style game.

games.description: A great passenger color sorting game begins with the Bus Stop Color Jam game! Sort the passengers by their color and get them into the buses. Once the buses are full, they will move to the destination point. Use power-ups when you need them. Over 400+ game levels are waiting for you! An entertaining Bus Stop Jam is beginning!
games.instructions: Use MOUSE and LEFT-CLICK Click over the passengers to start them to move.

games.description: Hop on an epic adventure with the Bug Heroes and help them defeat the menacing birds of the forest! Strategically link at least three symbols of the same colour to empower the Heroes with their special perks. Explore the lush green forests with your bug friends.
games.instructions: Connect as many symbols of the same colour as possible to complete levels and defeat enemy birds. Gather xp bottles and upgrade your bug heroes so they have even stronger perks.

games.description: Embark on a journey of survival in "Horseback Survival," where you, as Zohan, share an unbreakable connection with your horse, Badal. Born on the same day, your unique bond becomes a lifeline when a mysterious event leaves you in a coma. Navigate a zombie-infested world. Engage in intense combat with melee and ranged attacks, outsmart the undead by staying stealthy, and overcome obstacles with strategic running and jumping.
games.instructions: For Mobile: Joystick for movement, Jump button to jump For Desktop: A/D to move, Space for jump, and Shift to Run. Common: Click on the left side of the screen to perform a melee attack, hold and drag on the left side of the screen to aim and release to shoot

games.description: This game is perfect for puzzle enthusiasts. The fish is trapped on the beach, and you need to come up with a reasonable moving plan to release the fish one by one from the crowded scene. Strategize to free the trapped fish on the beach, testing your problem-solving skills. With numerous levels that increase in difficulty, it's a great way to pass the time.
games.instructions: Hold and drag to adjust the position of fish. Tap to move out.

games.description: After entering one of the rooms you have to find all the hidden objects. The names of the items you need to find will appear on the left side. You need to concentrate well and find all the objects in the room. You have to watch the time, because if it runs out it will be game over. Try to get the maximum points and three stars in every room.
games.instructions: After you see one of the objects, click on it with the mouse or tap on the screen.

games.description: Command heroes with unique abilities, gather natural resources to produce materials, then build and develop your military defenses. Enemy hordes will attack the village, challenging your strategic and tactical abilities to survive. Explore dark underground dungeons and battle against gigantic bosses! Features Build and upgrade your resources and heroes Set up defenses, hunt, cook, and much more Unlock new characters Action RPG and survival gameplay Beautiful epic fantasy pixel art
games.instructions: Use A and D to move, the mouse to attack, select abilities, and interact with structures by pressing the on-screen buttons.

games.description: Embark on an enchanting journey of matching gems! Dive into a realm filled with shimmering jewels, tactical maneuvers, and irresistible puzzle trials. Slide and place vibrant gems to unveil newfound powers. Confront challenges with diverse boosters to overcome obstacles and achieve higher scores.
games.instructions: Shift the blocks horizontally, clearing them upon completing a row. Blocks without support beneath will descend. With each move, the lower blocks ascend, ending the game upon reaching the top.

games.description: Ropeway Master is a new challenging puzzle game. You should utilize the rope to free everyone,control the rope, overcome the obstacles, and complete the demanding and unique puzzle game. The game is not difficult! Drag the rope to make a safe path, control the rope, and rescue everyone.Don't forget to avoid the obstacles along the way. If you play Rope Puzzle, make sure you do nothing. You will play for hours and linger.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Welcome to 'Runic Block Collapse'! Tap any block to clear connected blocks in a chain reaction. Removing one block costs 250 points. Removing 2 or more blocks earns points, with larger groups earning more per block. Reach the target score to advance. If you fail, start over. Enjoy endless fun!
games.instructions: Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game.

games.description: Save The Sheep offers an immersive mental challenge as you step into the shoes of a shepherd. Relentless wolves have invaded your flock, seeking to feast on your precious sheep. Safeguard your flock by strategically placing wooden stakes to separate them from the predators. Experience the electrifying thrill of rescuing sheep and demonstrate your unmatched intellect in this captivating game.
games.instructions: Slide to draw

games.description: Embark on a perilous journey in Offline FPS Royale, a brand new 3D shooter where you must fight for your life by eliminating every person you come across. You will get closer to finishing the map with every person you remove. Kill foes from every angle in battle royale games as a stealthy assassin with the most captivating sniper experience.
games.instructions: You must join the various game maps and finish each level while staying on the move and shooting all enemies before they kill you. Controls: Left click to shoot Right click to aim WASD to move Ctrl to Run Spacebar to Jump R Recharge

games.description: Welcome to Lulu’s Fashion World. Can you battle to become the top fashion designer? Collect stars, progress through cities and events. Choose from clothes you own from plenty categories. Style outfits your way and save them to use whenever you like. The combinations of clothing and makeup are at your fingertips to experiment and create unique trends that could become the new fashion trend. Experiment with new looks and create a fad. So, are you ready to be the new fashion icon ?
games.instructions: Choose a style and dress for the occasions. Become the best designer in Lulu’s Fashion World.

games.description: Wheel of Bingo has two parts. Part 1: Spin the wheel to match bingo numbers. To help the player, colored marks are drawn on the wheel to indicate their bingo numbers. For every match, the player gains points and a colored ball to be used in part 2. For a complete bingo line, many extra balls are awarded. Part 2: Drop balls to match colors in plinko. The point values shown at the bottom of the screen are base values, but are multiplied if there is a successful color match (GREEN MATCH X 5).
games.instructions: Part 1: Use the buttons labelled ' SPIN LEFT' and 'SPIN RIGHT' located below the wheel. Hold the button to power up the spin, which is indicated by the 'spin gauge' above the button. Part 2: Click and hold to position the ball at the top of the the plinko board. Release to launch the ball.

games.description: Welcome to FreeCell Solitaire! Dive into this classic card game where strategy and patience are key. With all cards visible from the start, plan your moves carefully to arrange them into the foundation piles by suit, from Ace to King. Use the free cells wisely to maneuver your way out of tight spots. Are you ready to tackle the challenge and clear the board? Play the Best Classic FreeCell Solitaire now and put your skills to the test!
games.instructions: The goal of the game is to move all of the cards onto the output stacks, starting with the ace of each suit and placing them in rising order from there. A card can only be moved onto another higher card if its rank is one higher and if it's of the opposite color. Blacks on reds and vice versa. Cards may also be placed in one of the four available FreeCells if not already occupied.

games.description: Welcome to Pin Detective - Mystery Mansion! A rich woman mysteriously vanished in a lavish mansion that was covered by the rumors of ghosts and dangerous monsters. A talented detective is committed to uncovering the mystery. By pulling the pin, you can collect clues that enlighten the truth. What happens to the billionaire? Why do the biological laboratory and so many alien animals exist in this mansion? Let’s use your brain to solve the puzzle to find it out.
games.instructions: ● Pull the pin to explore the mansion and uncover the mystery. ● Just a mistake can put you in danger and lose your life. ● Use coins to renovate the mansion and buy clothes.

games.description: Dive into "Flames & Fortune," a game inspired by Card Crawl, set in treacherous dungeons. Play as the Pyro-Paladin, mastering a deck of 54 cards to battle foes like goblins and dragons. Strategy determines survival and success brings gold to unlock new skills. Will you conquer the darkness for untold riches?
games.instructions: Draw cards using resources to defeat your enemies until there are no cards left in the deck. Each turn, new cards will be drawn until the 4 slots on the dashboard are filled. Equip the resource cards in your hands and backpack. Confront your enemies by casting spells at them, taking direct damage from them, or dampening it with a shield. Gather as many treasures as possible on your way out of the dungeon, and use the earned gold to unlock new Ability Cards.

games.description: “Hidden Object: Great Journey” is an engaging game that invites players to scour various themed levels for cleverly concealed items. With multiple modes, a lot of challenges, and a treasure trove of objects to find, this game promises endless fun for hidden object enthusiasts. Sharpen your observation skills and embark on a delightful search with every play!
games.instructions: Tap on hidden objects to reveal them. Tap on the differences between two pictures. Find the connection between two objects. Find the missing pieces.

games.description: 2020 Connect is the most addictive logic puzzle you’ve ever seen! The player’s task is to place at least four blocks with the same number on it next to each other so they get merged. 2020 Connect takes the best ideas of games like Merged and 2048 and turns it into a total blast. Merging more than four blocks will reward you with coins that later can be spend to purchase cool boosters. Will you be able to get the legendary 8192 blocks to merge?
games.instructions: Use your mouse to move the tiles into the right location in order to merge them.

games.description: Engage your mind with the classic puzzle game, Peg Solitaire. The objective is simple yet challenging: clear the board by jumping pegs over each other until only one peg remains. This timeless game tests your strategic thinking and planning skills, offering various levels of difficulty to keep you entertained.
games.instructions: Clear the board by jumping pegs over each other until only one peg remains.

games.description: A one-touch race, fly, crash game that sends you flying through the air in your car before you smash into everything in your path! Ramp Car Jumping is the most unusual challenge you’re likely to face this year. You literally jump off a ski jump in a car! Crazy speed Insane smashes Maximum heat And so many smashes, you’ll get crash burnout! Challenge your friends to an ol’ fashioned smash off! What’s the biggest crash you can imagine? Try now and watch it happen!
games.instructions: Keyboard: WASD/Arrow keys, space, enter Mouse

games.description: Fine tune your ride, keep your foot on the gas, dodge the endlessly varied obstacles, and try to keep out the way of your equally manic rivals in super-fast, super-exciting, psychedelic races that always offer something new and unexpected. Feel the need for speed?
games.instructions: USE Arrows keys for player movement.

games.description: See Match is a challenging match-3 puzzle game. Connect 3 or more of the same fishes horizontally or diagonally. The more fishes you match, the higher your score! Keep an eye on the time. You will fail to pass the level if you do not gather sufficient grids in time. The faster you complete the task, the more stars you earn! If you find yourself stuck, you can always use the special bonuses to help you.
games.instructions: Click to swap tiles and match three in a row!

games.description: Guess words of wisdom, proverbs and sayings in a fun brainteaser. Tap the words to make a phrase, and try to solve a riddle in 5 attempts using the color hints. As you progress, hidden phrases get longer, so you will need to apply all your logic and puzzle-solving skills to cope with the solve the riddles. Besides, such word games let you expand your vocabulary and learn foreign languages in a fun way. So, prove your skill as you decipher witty quotes and proverbs in a free word game online.
games.instructions: Tap the words to make a sentence, and decipher the phrase using color prompts. The words in their position are highlighted green. The words used in the sentence elsewhere are marked yellow. Gray words are not used in the riddle. Please, mind that words may be used twice in a phrase.

games.description: "Hyper Cars Ramp Crash" is a 3D stunt and crash simulation game with realistic physics and graphics. You can perform incredible stunts in many different modes with great looking cars. 7 different super-sport car models are waiting in the garage for you to try them. Open world, stunt modes and fall mode can be played in 1-player and 2-player modes.
games.instructions: If playing single: Move: "W,A,S,D" or "ARROW KEYS" NOS: "L-SHIFT" Restart car position: "R" Change camera view: "C" If playing two player: Player 1: Move: "W,A,S,D" NOS: "L-SHIFT" Restart car position: "R" Change camera view: "C" Player 2: Move: "ARROW KEYS" NOS: "N" Restart car position: "L" Change camera view: "U"

games.description: Match them all! Match all same pairs in the given time to win the game and earn coins. Use various powerups to match them faster. Spen your coins to decorate your house and unlock new houses.
games.instructions: Find identical pairs of objects and drag them into the round hatch to make them disappear. Clear the rubble and earn coins!

games.description: Lay hold of the land in PacXon New Realms, the long-awaited sequel to the 2007 classic PacXon Deluxe. Explore 192 challenging levels across 4 different locations. Dodge enemies as you seize chunks of territory in this thrilling twist on the original arcade adventure. Enjoy a revamped user interface, a fresh soundtrack, and nostalgic pixel art animations. Plus, unlock 4 - 6 unique character skins per location. Get ready for a captivating journey filled with new features and fun.
games.instructions: Create walls by running past the pellets, and close the loop to seize the area inside. In every level, you must capture at least 80% of the field to win. Check the progress bar at the top to see how you’re doing. Beware of ghostly mines - if they touch an unfinished wall, you lose a life! Each enemy follows a specific movement pattern. Look carefully and weave between them without getting hit! Keep an eye out for sweet treats; each of these power-ups provides a unique temporary boost.

games.description: Grim AI gathered amazing creatures at the circus arena and offered them the chance to compete for life here! Pick your character and get as much territory as you can! Run from your starting territory and return to add a chunk of space. Evade other characters or defeat them by stepping on their trail.
games.instructions: On mobiles - tap the screen, and your character will move in this direction. On the desktop, move your mouse how you want the character to move, or use WASD / arrow keys on the keyboard.
